  "url": "https://www.lovart.ai/zh/docs/edit-your-design/customize-your-canvas",
  "title": "Customize Your Canvas",
  "content": "The Select tool lets you pick, move, resize, and manage design elements on the infinite Canvas.\n\nThe Hand tool lets you navigate the infinite Canvas without risk of moving elements. Use it to pan across large layouts or reposition your view while reviewing work.\n\nYou can define a custom background color for your workspace.\n\nThe Layer panel lists every object in your project along with its history. Use it to locate elements across a busy Canvas and revisit earlier states.\n\nThe Generated Files panel lists every file the Agent has produced in the project, each with a download button.\n\nMini Map is a button on the Canvas that opens a miniature overview of your entire project. Use it to orient yourself in complex projects.",
